# AI-Empowered Governance Apps Development Rules

## Project Guidelines
- This is an MVP - prioritize simplicity over completeness
- Use TypeScript for type safety
- Follow React best practices
- Keep components focused and reusable

## Code Style
- Use functional components with hooks
- Prefer const over let
- Use async/await over promises where possible
- Keep functions small and focused

## Extension Specifics
- All storage goes through chrome.storage API
- No external API calls required
- Platform-independent (works with any AI chat)
- Clipboard-based workflow

## Testing
- Manual testing checklist in plan document
- Calculations must match Python reference implementation
- Validate all JSON inputs/outputs

